20132004\n| September 27, 2003\n| May 8, 2004\n| #99\n| 7.39<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet |url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/Web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=060204_11 |website=ABC Medianet |publisher=The Walt Disney Company |via=The Internet Archive |accessdate=October 15, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930155240/http://www.abcmedianet.com/Web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=060204_11 |archivedate=September 30, 2007 }}</ref>\n|-\n| 49\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2004\u20132005\n| October 16, 2004\n| June 18, 2005\n| #96\n| 6.93<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet |url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/pressrel/dispDNR.html?id=060105_05 |website=ABC Medianet |publisher=The Walt Disney Company |via=The Internet Archive |accessdate=October 15, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310210208/http://www.abcmedianet.com/pressrel/dispDNR.html?id=060105_05 |archivedate=March 10, 2007 }}</ref>\n|-\n| 50\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2005\u20132006\n| November 5, 2005\n| July 8, 2006\n| #137\n| 5.30<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet|url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/Web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052306_07|website=ABC Medianet|publisher=The Walt Disney Company|date=May 23, 2006|accessdate=October 15, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| 51\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2006\u20132007\n| December 16, 2006\n| August 4, 2007\n| #208<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet|url=http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=060507_05|website=ABC Medianet|publisher=The Walt Disney Company|date=June 5, 2007|accessdate=October 15, 2013}}</ref>\n| 4.28<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet|url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/Web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=082107_08|website=ABC Medianet|publisher=The Walt Disney Company|date=August 21, 2007|accessdate=October 15, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| 52\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2007\u20132008\n| December 22, 2007\n| December 20, 2008\n| #172<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet|url=http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052808_06|website=ABC Medianet|publisher=The Walt Disney Company|date=May 28, 2008|accessdate=October 15, 2013}}</ref>\n| 4.01<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC Medianet|url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/Web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=080508_05|website=ABC Medianet|publisher=The Walt Disney Company|date=August 5, 2008|accessdate=October 15, 2013}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n===Emmy Awards===\n\n====Won====\n#Best Individual Program of the Year (''Operation Undersea'', 1955)\n#Best Television Film Editing ([[Lynn Harrison]], Grant K. Smith, ''Operation Undersea'', 1955)\n#Best Action or Adventure Series (1956)\n#Best Producer \u2013 Film Series (Walt Disney, 1956)\n#Outstanding Program Achievement in the Field of Children's Programming (1963)\n#Outstanding Program Achievements in Entertainment (Walt Disney, 1965)\n#Special Classification of Outstanding Program and Individual Achievement \u2013 Programs ([[Ron W. Miller|Ron Miller]], executive producer, 1971)\n#Outstanding Main Title Design (1998)\n\n====Nominated====\n#Best Television Film Editing (Chester W. Schaeffer, \"Davy Crockett: Indian Fighter\", 1955)\n#Best Single Program of the Year (\"Davy Crockett and River Pirates\", 1956)\n#Best Musical Contribution for Television (Oliver Wallace, 1957)\n#Outstanding Program Achievement in the Field of Children's Programming (1962)\n#Outstanding Program Achievements in the Fields of Variety and Music \u2013 Variety (1962)\n#Outstanding Children's Program (Walt Disney, Ron Miller (''Further Adventures of Gallagher'', 1966)\n#Outstanding Achievement in Children's Programming \u2013 Programs (Ron Miller, executive producer, 1969)\n#Outstanding Achievement in Children's Programming \u2013 Programs (Ron Miller, executive producer, 1970)\n#Special Classification of Outstanding Program and Individual Achievement \u2013 General Programming (Ron Miller, producer, 1972)\n#Special Classification of Outstanding Program Achievement (Ron Miller, executive producer, 1977)\n#Outstanding Children's Progr